ChangeLog
---------

Release 2:
 - Added word-wrapping.
 - Added paging, i.e. display [MORE] prompt when more than a page of text is
   output between input prompts.
 - Clear console before the story file starts executing.
 - Make a better effort to restore the original current working directory when
   Z-MIM exits.
 - Minor improvements to the interactive debugger.
 - Cosmetic improvements to code and README.

Release 1:
 - Initial public beta.
